# Technology Stack

## Core Framework
- **Next.js 15** - React framework with App Router for optimal performance and SEO
- **React 19** - Latest React version with new features and optimizations

## Content Management
- **Payload CMS 3.0** - Headless CMS for dynamic content management
- **PostgreSQL** - Primary database with Payload Postgres adapter
- **GraphQL** - API layer for data fetching

## Frontend & Styling
- **TypeScript 5.5** - Type-safe development
- **Tailwind CSS** - Utility-first CSS framework
- **Radix UI** - Accessible component primitives
- **Lucide React** - Icon library
- **Embla Carousel** - Touch-friendly carousel component

## Development Tools
- **Biome** - Fast linter and formatter
- **PostCSS** - CSS processing
- **Sharp** - Image optimization
- **Cross-env** - Environment variable management

## Deployment & Storage
- **Vercel Blob** - File storage for media uploads
- **Cloud Storage Plugin** - Payload integration for cloud storage

## Key Features
- **SEO Optimized**: Built-in Next.js SEO capabilities
- **Image Optimization**: Automatic image processing and optimization
- **Type Safety**: Full TypeScript coverage
- **Performance**: React 19 compiler and Next.js optimizations
- **Accessibility**: Radix UI components ensure WCAG compliance
- **Catalan Language**: Primary language with i18n-ready architecture

## Development Workflow
- **Package Manager**: pnpm for fast, efficient dependency management
- **Code Quality**: Biome for linting and formatting
- **Database**: Docker-based PostgreSQL for local development
